            <h3 style="color: #CC0000">LEMON TREE HOTEL</h3>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Lemon Tree Hotel, Gangtok is set in the lap of the enchanting eastern Himalayan range, offering captivating views of the serene valley. Conveniently located just 10 minutes away from MG Marg, the refreshing hotel is designed in traditional Sikkimese style architecture, with stylish wood frontages, arched windows, and red and yellow sloping roofs. A vibrant lobby ushers you into 80 stylish and spacious rooms that help you unwind with their fresh and bright interiors, smart in-room amenities, refreshing services and a close to home comfort. The hotel houses a multi-cuisine coffee shop – Citrus Café and soon-to-open hip-recreation bar-Slounge, rejuvenating spa- Fresco, full equipped gym, besides an outdoor swimming pool, to keep you feeling fresh-as-a-lemon. An idyllic place of stay for both business and leisure, the hotel is about 3 hours from Nathula Pass, on the Indo-Chinese border and is in close proximity to Kanchenjanga National Park, the UNESCO World Heritage Site.<br />
                 <h3 style="color: #CC0000">HOTEL PARADISO</h3>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
Located in Kalimpong, Hotel Paradiso features a terrace. There is a restaurant serving Indian cuisine, and free private parking is available.All units in the hotel are equipped with a flat-screen TV. Featuring a private bathroom, rooms at Hotel Paradiso also provide guests with free WiFi.A à la carte breakfast is available daily at the accommodation
The area is popular for cycling, and bike hire and car hire are available at Hotel Paradiso.
Speaking Bengali, English and Hindi, staff at the 24-hour front desk can help you plan your stay.
The nearest airport is Bagdogra Airport, 78 km from the hotel.<br />
                 <h3 style="color: #CC0000">GIG TEA HOUSE</h3>
                 &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
                 Ging Tea House provides Victorian style accommodation with free WiFi.
A continental breakfast can be enjoyed at the property. It also houses a dining room for long lunches, 3 course evening meals and good wine. Guests can enjoy bonfires and indoor board games.
The country house offers a children's playground.
Guests can indulge in trekking and hiking through marked trails in the tea gardens and also tea plantation and tea making process guided tour ending in a tea tasting session.
Tiger Hill is 32 km from the accommodation. The nearest airport is Bagdogra, 77 km from Ging Tea House.<br />
